msgid "Run `cargo build` to make sure it compiles."
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/cargo-and-crates-io/cargo-check-for-faster-checking.md:22
#: src/rust-2018/cargo-and-crates-io/cargo-check-for-faster-checking.md:40
msgid "Repeat 1-2 as needed."
