msgid "Improved error messages"
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/the-compiler/improved-error-messages.md:5
msgid ""
"We're always working on error improvements, and there are little "
"improvements in almost every Rust version, but in Rust 1.12, a significant "
"overhaul of the error message system was created."
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/the-compiler/improved-error-messages.md:9
msgid "For example, here's some code that produces an error:"
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/the-compiler/improved-error-messages.md:21
msgid "Here's the error in Rust 1.11:"
